LogicalColumn.name: Revenue Range

Expr.name: Expr
Expr.ExprText: CASE WHEN "%1" = 'AAG Account' OR "%1" = 'Fin Account' THEN CASE WHEN "%2" < 500 THEN 'A: 0-500' WHEN "%2" < 2500 THEN 'B: 500-2500' WHEN "%2" < 10000 THEN 'C: 2500-10K' WHEN "%2" <= 50000 THEN 'D: 10K-50K' WHEN NOT "%2" IS NULL THEN 'E: >50K' END ELSE CASE WHEN "%2" < 500 THEN 'A: 0-500' WHEN "%2" < 2500 THEN 'B: 500-2500' WHEN "%2" < 10000 THEN 'C: 2500-10K' WHEN "%2" < 50000 THEN 'D: 10K-50K' WHEN "%2" <= 100000 THEN 'E: 50K-100K' WHEN NOT "%2" IS NULL THEN 'F: >100K' END END
Expr.ExprTextDesc: CASE WHEN "Oracle Data Warehouse"."Catalog"."dbo"."W_ASSET_D"."ASSET_TYPE_I" = 'AAG Account' OR "Oracle Data Warehouse"."Catalog"."dbo"."W_ASSET_D"."ASSET_TYPE_I" = 'Fin Account' THEN CASE WHEN "Oracle Data Warehouse"."Catalog"."dbo"."Fact_W_ASSET_F_FINS"."REVENUE" < 500 THEN 'A: 0-500' WHEN "Oracle Data Warehouse"."Catalog"."dbo"."Fact_W_ASSET_F_FINS"."REVENUE" < 2500 THEN 'B: 500-2500' WHEN "Oracle Data Warehouse"."Catalog"."dbo"."Fact_W_ASSET_F_FINS"."REVENUE" < 10000 THEN 'C: 2500-10K' WHEN "Oracle Data Warehouse"."Catalog"."dbo"."Fact_W_ASSET_F_FINS"."REVENUE" <= 50000 THEN 'D: 10K-50K' WHEN NOT "Oracle Data Warehouse"."Catalog"."dbo"."Fact_W_ASSET_F_FINS"."REVENUE" IS NULL THEN 'E: >50K' END ELSE CASE WHEN "Oracle Data Warehouse"."Catalog"."dbo"."Fact_W_ASSET_F_FINS"."REVENUE" < 500 THEN 'A: 0-500' WHEN "Oracle Data Warehouse"."Catalog"."dbo"."Fact_W_ASSET_F_FINS"."REVENUE" < 2500 THEN 'B: 500-2500' WHEN "Oracle Data Warehouse"."Catalog"."dbo"."Fact_W_ASSET_F_FINS"."REVENUE" < 10000 THEN 'C: 2500-10K' WHEN "Oracle Data Warehouse"."Catalog"."dbo"."Fact_W_ASSET_F_FINS"."REVENUE" < 50000 THEN 'D: 10K-50K' WHEN "Oracle Data Warehouse"."Catalog"."dbo"."Fact_W_ASSET_F_FINS"."REVENUE" <= 100000 THEN 'E: 50K-100K' WHEN NOT "Oracle Data Warehouse"."Catalog"."dbo"."Fact_W_ASSET_F_FINS"."REVENUE" IS NULL THEN 'F: >100K' END END

Expr.ExprTextDesc: CASE WHEN "Oracle Data Warehouse"."Catalog"."dbo"."Fact_W_ASSET_F_FINS"."REVENUE" = 0 THEN 'B: 0-10%' WHEN "Oracle Data Warehouse"."Catalog"."dbo"."Fact_W_ASSET_F_FINS"."REVENUE" IS NULL THEN 'Unspecified' WHEN 100.0d * "Oracle Data Warehouse"."Catalog"."dbo"."Fact_W_ASSET_F_FINS"."PROFIT" / "Oracle Data Warehouse"."Catalog"."dbo"."Fact_W_ASSET_F_FINS"."REVENUE" < 0 THEN 'A: <0%' WHEN 100.0d * "Oracle Data Warehouse"."Catalog"."dbo"."Fact_W_ASSET_F_FINS"."PROFIT" / "Oracle Data Warehouse"."Catalog"."dbo"."Fact_W_ASSET_F_FINS"."REVENUE" < 10 THEN 'B: 0-10%' WHEN 100.0d * "Oracle Data Warehouse"."Catalog"."dbo"."Fact_W_ASSET_F_FINS"."PROFIT" / "Oracle Data Warehouse"."Catalog"."dbo"."Fact_W_ASSET_F_FINS"."REVENUE" < 20 THEN 'C: 10-20%' WHEN 100.0d * "Oracle Data Warehouse"."Catalog"."dbo"."Fact_W_ASSET_F_FINS"."PROFIT" / "Oracle Data Warehouse"."Catalog"."dbo"."Fact_W_ASSET_F_FINS"."REVENUE" <= 30 THEN 'D: 20-30%' WHEN NOT 100.0d * "Oracle Data Warehouse"."Catalog"."dbo"."Fact_W_ASSET_F_FINS"."PROFIT" / "Oracle Data Warehouse"."Catalog"."dbo"."Fact_W_ASSET_F_FINS"."REVENUE" IS NULL THEN 'E: >30%' END
